===Etymology===
From {{der|en|sa|यक्ष}}.
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# {{lb|en|Indian mythology}} A [[kind]] of [[supernatural]] [[being]];  can be a malevolent [[demon]] or a beneficent [[tutelary deity]].
# {{lb|en|Southeast Asian|_|mythology}} A [[kind]] of [[supernatural]] [[being]], [[often]] [[depict]]ed as [[have|having]] [[supernatural]] [[power]], [[great]] [[strength]], and [[frightening]] [[appearance]]; can be a malevolent [[demon]] or a beneficent [[tutelary deity]].
